        stringBuilder.append("            \"title\": \"Recorded Webinar: How to migrate to the new Kayako\",\n");
        stringBuilder.append("            \"contents\": \"<p><a href=\\\"http://learn.kayako.com/recorded-webinar-how-to-migrate-the-new-kayako\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\"></a>Great news - we&#39;re beginning to migrate our\\n  customers&#39; data over to their new Kayako accounts. Last week, we\\n  hosted a webinar to share our migration process with our\\n  customers.</p>\\n  <p>For this special presentation,\\n  Kayako&#39;s<strong><span> </span>Customer Success Consultant\\n  Gary McGrath</strong> walked us through:</p>\\n  <ul>\\n    <li>How to prepare your data for migration</li>\\n    <li>Testing the new platform and going live</li>\\n    <li>How to replicate business rules and defaults after\\n    migrating</li>\\n  </ul>\\n  <p><a href=\\\"http://learn.kayako.com/recorded-webinar-how-to-migrate-the-new-kayako\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\"><img class=\\\"fr-dib fr-draggable\\\" src=\\\"https://support.kayako.com/base/media/url/ugkyUpliFqtEbuAGXRgceBj6uTGt67Ba\\\" style=\\\"width: 537px; height: 264px;\\\"></a><br></p>\\n  <h2>Getting ready to upgrade from Kayako Classic?</h2>\\n  <p>Find answers to all your questions here.</p>\\n  <p>   - <a href=\\\"http://www.slideshare.net/kayakocom/webinar-deck-how-to-migrate-to-the-new-kayako\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Migration webinar slides</a></p>\\n  <p>   - <a href=\\\"https://support.kayako.com/article/1206-understanding-how-the-upgrade-process-works\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Understanding how the migration process\\n  works</a></p>\\n  <p>   - <a href=\\\"https://support.kayako.com/api/v1/articles/1206/attachments/489167/download\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Kayako Migration Worksheet</a></p>\\n  <p>   - <a href=\\\"https://support.kayako.com/section/253-upgrades-migration\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Upgrades &amp; Migration User Guides</a></p>\\n  <h2>Want to learn more about the new Kayako?</h2>\\n  <p>Sign up for a <a href=\\\"https://www.kayako.com/product/demo\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">personal demo</a> of the new product here, or\\n  check out our <a href=\\\"https://www.kayako.com/product/demo\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">recorded webinar specifically for existing\\n  customers</a> considering an upgrade.</p>\",\n");
