        stringBuilder.append("            \"uuid\": \"3e69d2d3-bfa4-5f02-9434-8cd6df482920\",\n");
        stringBuilder.append("            \"title\": \"Continued support subscription plans for Kayako Download legacy license customers\",\n");
        stringBuilder.append("            \"contents\": \"<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">When we launched the new, cloud-only Kayako in July\\n  2016, we also announced an end-of-life (EOL) for Kayako Download\\n  (July 2017, with 6 months of security fixes).</p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Since then, <a href=\\\"https://support.kayako.com/article/1284-kayako-download-continued-support\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">we announced the cancellation of those end-of-life\\n  plans</a> and that we will continue to support and develop Kayako\\n  Download (aka, Kayako Classic) alongside the new Kayako.</p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">As part of this, we have also introduced new a new\\n  continued support subscription for Kayako Download perpetual\\n  customers who want to continue receiving access to support and\\n  new product updates.</p>\\n  <h1 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">The new continued support plans</h1>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Kayako Download perpetual license customers who want\\n  to continue receiving support and access to new updates will need\\n  to renew onto a new continued support subscription:</p>\\n  <ul>\\n    <li dir=\\\"ltr\\\">$15 per staff user per month for Kayako Case and\\n    Kayako Engage, billed annually</li>\\n    <li dir=\\\"ltr\\\">$20 per staff user per month for Kayako Fusion,\\n    billed annually</li>\\n  </ul>\\n  <p><span style=\\\"background-color: transparent; text-align: initial;\\\">An\\n  additional 10% discount is available for two-year renewals made\\n  upfront.</span></p>\\n  <p><span style=\\\"background-color: transparent; text-align: initial;\\\">In addition\\n  to securing ongoing development, new capabilities, updates and\\n  support, this subscription also guarantees your discount pricing\\n  for the new Kayako in the cloud, whenever you choose to upgrade.\\n  When you decide to upgrade, you&#39;ll just pay the same price for\\n  each of your staff user.</span></p>\\n  <h1>Questions answered</h1>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Why do I need to pay more for my renewal?</h3>\\n  <p>In short, so that we can sustainably develop and support\\n  Kayako Download.</p>\\n  <p>The reason why we originally announced an end-of-life for\\n  Kayako Download was because we could no longer sustain supporting\\n  and developing it for our customers on legacy license plans, such\\n  as yours, which we have historically grandfathered.</p>\\n  <p>This is for a few reasons, including the increased capability\\n  breadth and added complexity of the Kayako Download product, and\\n  the declining number of our customers who have opted or stuck\\n  with for Kayako Download (on-premise) vs Kayako in the cloud.</p>\\n  <p>That&#39;s why we initially decided to end-of-life the product.\\n  However, following this announcement, we were contacted by a\\n  large number of customers who asked us to put together tailored\\n  extended support contracts for them. We took a few of these\\n  conversations forward and had a lot of take up. </p>\\n  <p>Off the back of this, we created a new business model around\\n  Kayako Download, which resulted in these new continued support\\n  plans. That&#39;s what we are now offering to all existing Kayako\\n  Download customers.</p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">What happens if I don&#39;t renew onto the new\\n  continued support plans?</h3>\\n  <p>There is no obligation to renew. If you do not wish to sign\\n  up<span> </span>to<span> </span>the continued support\\n  plans, you can continue using your Kayako Download perpetual\\n  license, but your access to new product releases and Kayako\\n  support will lapse at the earlier of your license expiry date, or\\n  July 2017 (the original end-of-life date).</p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">What is a staff user, and how does the licensing\\n  work?</h3>\\n  <p>A <em>staff user</em> is anyone who needs to log in to the\\n  staff or admin area of your Kayako and support your customers\\n  (replying to tickets, accepting live chats, etc).</p>\\n  <p>You need one staff user license for every enabled staff user\\n  account in your Kayako installation. You can see how many you\\n  have today in your admin control panel, under Staff and then\\n  Manage Staff.</p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">How can I renew an &#39;unlimited staff user&#39;\\n  license?</h3>\\n  <p>The new continued support plans are priced per staff user. If\\n  you have an &#39;unlimited staff user&#39; license, you&#39;ll need to renew\\n  for the number of staff user accounts you need in your\\n  Kayako.</p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Will I be able to add new staff users to my\\n  license?</h3>\\n  <p>You can add any number of staff users to your license, and\\n  would only need to pay the pro-rata difference. For example, if\\n  you were 7 months into your 1 year subscription and you added a\\n  new staff user, you&#39;d pay for the remaining 5 months for your\\n  term. </p>\\n  <p>You can also reduce the number of staff users on your license,\\n  but these changes won&#39;t affect your billing until your\\n  renewal.</p>\\n  <p>You no longer need to upgrade your license level in lots of 10\\n  staff users at a time. If you just need one extra, you only need\\n  to add 1 staff user to your subscription.</p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">What if I want to upgrade to the new Kayako?</h3>\\n  <p>As well as securing the cheapest upgrade path to the new\\n  Kayako (because you&#39;ll pay the same you do on the continued\\n  support plan), you can still upgrade to the new Kayako, at a time\\n  that suits you. <a href=\\\"https://support.kayako.com/article/1275-upgrading-to-the-new-kayako-for-kayako-classic-customers\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Find out more</a> here.</p>\\n  <h3>I&#39;m waiting to be upgraded to the new Kayako - how does this\\n  change my options?</h3>\\n  <p>We&#39;re sorry it has taken a while for us to get going with the\\n  upgrades. When we launched the new Kayako, we weren&#39;t expecting\\n  the amount of interest from Kayako Download customers to upgrade.\\n  So, we took the time to pause and improve the speed of the\\n  process, including better documentation and automated upgrade\\n  tools.</p>\\n  <p>We&#39;ll be back up very shortly. We&#39;re doing new trials on the\\n  new migration process now. You&#39;ll certainly hear from us\\n  in<span> </span>the coming couple<span> </span>of\\n  months.</p>\\n  <p>You may still want to consider the new continued support plans\\n  for your Kayako Download license today. </p>\\n  <p>By renewing onto those plans, you will lock in your discounted\\n  pricing and will secure the cheapest upgrade path to the new\\n  Kayako. Customers upgrading to the new Kayako from Kayako\\n  Download will get access to the <strong>Loyalty</strong> plan,\\n  which has all the capabilities of our top\\n  <strong>Enterprise</strong> plan that are available today.\\n  Instead of paying $90 per staff per user for the Enterprise plan,\\n  you&#39;ll only need to pay whatever you pay on your continued\\n  support plan.</p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">What happens if I cancel my continued support\\n  subscription in the future?</h3>\\n  <p>If you let your subscription lapse, you would lose application\\n  access (i.e. the ability to reply to and update tickets), but\\n  you&#39;d still have all of your data. </p>\\n  <p>Your license key is tied to the subscription plan. Securing\\n  the regular<span> </span>renewals while customers are still\\n  using Kayako<span> </span>is a key part of us being able to\\n  continue developing and supporting Kayako Download.</p>\\n  <p>If you have any specific concerns around business continuity,\\n  <a href=\\\"mailto:classic@kayako.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">contact us to\\n  discuss</a>.</p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">My license is still active - do I need to renew\\n  onto the new plans?</h3>\\n  <p>If you renew onto the new continued support plans while your\\n  license is still active, you&#39;ll receive an additional discount\\n  for the lifetime of your subscription. Log in to <a href=\\\"https://my.kayako.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">my.kayako.com</a> and\\n  click <strong>View options and renew</strong> under your\\n  license to find out more.</p>\\n  <p>Any support subscription that is active on your license will\\n  be credited back to you, pro-rata. For example, if you have 3\\n  months of support remaining on your license and you renew onto\\n  the continued support plans early, you&#39;ll receive that value back\\n  in a credit. You won&#39;t double-pay for anything.</p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">I need a lot of staff users, so this model won&#39;t\\n  work for me</h3>\\n  <p>If you need a large number of staff users, we&#39;re happy to\\n  tailor a proposal for you on the continued support plans - drop\\n  us a line with your license ID or domain name: <a href=\\\"mailto:%20classic@kayako.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">classic@kayako.com</a></p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">I&#39;m an NPO, charity or academic institution - do I\\n  receive a discount?</h3>\\n  <p>This depends on your license type and the discounts you may\\n  have already received. Please contact us for more information:\\n  <a href=\\\"mailto:%20classic@kayako.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">classic@kayako.com</a></p>\\n  <h1 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">What next for Kayako Classic</h1>\\n  <p>In the last year, we&#39;ve released:</p>\\n  <ul>\\n    <li>A new, responsive, mobile-friendly support center</li>\\n    <li>The ability to merge user accounts</li>\\n    <li>{placeholder} support for ticket replies</li>\\n    <li>Rich text ticket replies</li>\\n    <li>Custom field data now available for use in ticket\\n    notification templates</li>\\n    <li>Improved searching in the support center</li>\\n    <li>Your customers now have the ability to CC other recipients\\n    when creating tickets from support center</li>\\n    <li>Significant speed and relevancy improvements to search in\\n    the staff area</li>\\n    <li>Changes to improve auto-threading and conversation views in\\n    email services like Gmail</li>\\n    <li>Significant email parsing improvements, including MS\\n    Outlook email attachment (.msg, .eml) parsing</li>\\n    <li>Improved localization support</li>\\n    <li>More than 20 security enhancements and fixes</li>\\n    <li>100s of other smaller improvements and fixes</li>\\n  </ul>\\n  <p>Our focus is to continue to focus improving and developing\\n  what Kayako Classic is already good at: powerful and flexible and\\n  customisable workflows, and a productivity suite to make even\\n  small teams productive dealing with large numbers of support\\n  tickets.</p>\\n  <p>While we don&#39;t have a public roadmap for any of our products,\\n  in the coming year, we&#39;ll be looking closely at (among other\\n  things) some popular feature requests, including: further\\n  searching improvements, keyboard shortcuts, ticket filtering in\\n  the support center, popular workflow feature  requests such\\n  as the ability to permanently close support tickets and email\\n  parser failure alerts, SLA improvements and the ability to\\n  leverage custom field data in rules in Kayako.</p>\\n  <p><a href=\\\"mailto:classic@kayako.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">We&#39;d love\\n  to hear your feedback</a> about what you&#39;d like to see.</p>\\n  <h1 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">What next for your license renewal</h1>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Renewing</h3>\\n  <p>To renew your Kayako Download license onto the continued\\n  support plans, visit <a href=\\\"https://my.kayako.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">my.kayako.com</a> and click <strong>View options and\\n  renew</strong> under your license. You&#39;ll be able to\\n  configure your renewal and pay by card online.</p>\\n  <p>If you need a quotation or would like to pay by bank transfer,\\n  please contact us: <a href=\\\"mailto:%20classic@kayako.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">classic@kayako.com</a></p>\\n  <h3 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Questions</h3>\\n  <p>Our team is happy to answer any questions about your Kayako\\n  Download license, the new Kayako and the continued support plans.\\n  Send us an email: <a href=\\\"mailto:%20classic@kayako.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">classic@kayako.com</a></p>\",\n");
