        stringBuilder.append("            \"uuid\": \"fb2480a5-2c69-5137-b13a-ce13db22db1d\",\n");
        stringBuilder.append("            \"title\": \"Introducing the new Kayako\",\n");
        stringBuilder.append("            \"contents\": \"<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Today, I’m really excited to announce the launch of\\n  the new Kayako, a brand new product, platform, and user\\n  experience that has been redesigned and reimagined for delivering\\n  modern, personal customer service.</p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">We’ve listened carefully to your feedback, and\\n  thought hard about what businesses should be doing to improve\\n  their customer service instead of just managing the existing\\n  demands on their team. </p>\\n  <h2 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Kayako helps you get better at customer\\n  service</h2>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">We exist to help businesses to get better at\\n  customer service. To deliver effortless, personal, and memorable\\n  customer support. To transform your team from a cost-center, into\\n  a profit-center. To become so good at customer service that it\\n  becomes your competitive advantage. </p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">And it starts with reimagining the traditional\\n  customer service helpdesk. </p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Kayako is a customer service platform that unifies\\n  your support channels, your customer information and your team -\\n  so you can work better together to truly understand your customer\\n  and support them where they are. </p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">With the new Kayako, you can:</p>\\n  <ul>\\n    <li dir=\\\"ltr\\\">\\n      <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Offer an effortless customer experience with\\n      unified, multi-channel cases </p>\\n    </li>\\n    <li dir=\\\"ltr\\\">\\n      <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Understand your customer like never before with\\n      user timelines including more context with plug and play\\n      integrations</p>\\n    </li>\\n    <li dir=\\\"ltr\\\">\\n      <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Work closely with your team with built-in\\n      collaboration tools</p>\\n    </li>\\n    <li dir=\\\"ltr\\\">\\n      <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Be more productive with customizable automations\\n      and workflows </p>\\n    </li>\\n  </ul>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><a href=\\\"https://www.kayako.com/blog/kayako-launches-unified-customer-service-platform/\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Read more about why we’ve designed the new\\n  Kayako.</a></p>\\n  <h2 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">What this means for you</h2>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">If you’re new to Kayako — welcome! We hope you’ll\\n  love it. <a href=\\\"http://kayako.com/free-trial\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Sign up for your free 14-day trial</a>, and let us\\n  know your thoughts. </p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">If you’re an existing Kayako customers, please log\\n  into <a href=\\\"https://my.kayako.com/#upgrade\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">my.kayako.com</a> for more information on how and when\\n  you’ll be able to upgrade. You can also view a <a href=\\\"https://support.kayako.com/article/1140-understanding-what-s-changed-in-the-new-kayako\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">comprehensive list of changes in this help center\\n  article</a>. Finally, feel free to sign up for a free trial to\\n  take it for a test drive.</p>\\n  <h2 dir=\\\"ltr\\\">We’re here to help</h2>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Thanks for being part of our journey so far — I’m\\n  looking forward to our next adventure together! </p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Thanks,</p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Varun Shoor<br>\\n  CEO, Kayako</p>\\n  <p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">p.s. Our Kayako 4 self-service articles will\\n  continue to be hosted here on support.kayako.com. You can\\n  identify them by the “Kayako Classic” flag at the top! </p>\",\n");
